ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然冇點解唔on9下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"我諗無人特登show俾人知佢醒目啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多數都係機緣巧合先發現 嘩 原來佢咁醒目唔係平時on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5a858082902f87f90a6acd3b09ca72d53f974","tid":2175582,"uid":199102,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"有個女仔朋友睇落好蠢又大頭蝦 <br />\n呢樣嗰樣唔記得咁<br />\n平地都可以自己跌親嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但後尾發現原來佢係扮緊蠢<br />\n佢個人不知幾叻幾聰明<br />\n<br />\n聰明嘅女人最叻扮蠢<br />\n真係蠢嘅女人先會扮聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc3eed2a6d388d0c308d621550c5e96471a81f8","tid":2175582,"uid":366474,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係特登扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樣問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人睇樣覺得我傻下傻下<br />\n識耐左就會話：乜你原來咁聰明㗎，睇唔出喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係朋友公司翻part time<br />\n基本上個個同事都勁熱心教我做野<br />\n甚至幫我做埋<br />\n話覺得我傻下傻下唔識做(其實我識）<br />\n當然有拒絕佢地<br />\n但佢地第一句就會話：唔好扮啦，我知你唔識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755f412318aac2109b8ae8f890b8b6c519095221","tid":2175582,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0b5a858082902f87f90a6acd3b09ca72d53f974","tid":2175582,"uid":199102,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"有個女仔朋友睇落好蠢又大頭蝦 <br />\n呢樣嗰樣唔記得咁<br />\n平地都可以自己跌親嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但後尾發現原來佢係扮緊蠢<br />\n佢個人不知幾叻幾聰明<br />\n<br />\n聰明嘅女人最叻扮蠢<br />\n真係蠢嘅女人先會扮聰明<img s